OL,7,FAn independent report into the PFAS
OL,8,Flevels of Jersey's surface water and
OL,9,Fgroundwater has found there to be no
OL,10,F"immediate risk to the health of the
OL,11,Fbroader population".
OL,13,FHowever, it has confirmed that the
OL,14,Fextent of affected groundwater near
OL,15,Fthe airport to be larger than
OL,16,Fpreviously thought.
