OL,7,FThis is referred to as the 'plume
OL,8,Farea' and officers for Infrastructure
OL,9,Fand Environment are now identifying
OL,10,Fproperties which draw water from
OL,11,Fboreholes within the newly expanded
OL,12,Fzone.
OL,14,FHome and landowners of any impacted
OL,15,Fproperties will be contacted directly
OL,16,Fand provided with individual
OL,17,Fenvironmental health advice.
OL,19,FGroundwater is defined as water that
OL,20,Flies below the surface while surface
OL,21,Fwater is classed as ponds and streams.
