OL,7,FJersey's Minister for the Environment,
OL,8,FDeputy Steve Luce, says: "PFAS is not
OL,9,Fjust in Jersey, it's everywhere. But
OL,10,Fwe're coming up with scientific,
OL,11,Fevidence-based solutions to deal with
OL,12,Fit.
OL,14,F"We commissioned this report to give
OL,15,Fus a better understanding of where
OL,16,FPFAS is and what we can do about it.
OL,18,F"It is a detailed report on a complex
OL,19,Fmatter and its findings deserve proper
OL,20,Fconsideration."
