OL,7,FThe full 651-page hydrogeological
OL,8,Freport was published today (1 May) and
OL,9,Fwas compiled by Arcadis - a company
OL,10,Fwhich specialises in environmental
OL,11,Frestoration.
OL,13,FThe company visited the island on four
OL,14,Foccasions between July 2023 and May
OL,15,F2024 to sample a wide range of water.
OL,17,FPFAS levels were checked across the St
OL,18,FOuen's Bay and Upper Pont Marquet -
OL,19,Fboth impacted areas which Jersey Water
OL,20,Fno longer draws water from.
