OL,7,FWhat is PFAS?
OL,9,FPFAS and PFOS: What is the difference?
OL,11,FPFAS contaminated several private
OL,12,Fwater supplies in the west of Jersey
OL,13,Fafter leaking from the airport in the
OL,14,F1990s, where it was being used in
OL,15,Ffirefighting foams.
OL,17,FOne of the report's key findings
OL,18,Fstates "significant PFAS
OL,19,Fcontamination" remains under the Fire
OL,20,FTraining Ground at Jersey Airport.
