OL,7,FIt recommends that Jersey's government
OL,8,Fcontinue targeted monitoring to help
OL,9,Ffill in gaps with data.
OL,11,FFurther testing and monitoring will
OL,12,Ftake place over the summer months to
OL,13,Fmonitor the movement of PFAS from and
OL,14,Faround the airport site.
OL,16,FThe Minister will now review the
OL,17,Freport's findings and produce a full
OL,18,Fresponse by 12 June.
